    <item>
      <title>How to Evaluate a Dialectical Argument</title>
      <link>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/texts/how-to-evaluate-a-dialectical-argument/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://emsenn.net/library/domains/humanities/domains/philosophy/domains/western/domains/marxism/texts/how-to-evaluate-a-dialectical-argument/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;strong&gt;how-to&lt;/strong&gt; text. It gives a practical procedure for evaluating&#xA;a specific argument.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;goal&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#goal&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;Goal&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Determine whether an argument uses dialectics as method, not only as&#xA;style.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;steps&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#steps&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;Steps&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-isolate-the-object&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#1-isolate-the-object&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;1) Isolate the object&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Write one sentence naming the object under analysis (institution,&#xA;concept, social relation, historical process).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If the object is unclear, stop. No dialectical evaluation is possible.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
